## Priority Action Plan

| Priority | Action | Effort | Impact |
|---|---|---|---|
| 🔴 **P1** | Add "Single vs Multi-Branch" toggle to Company Profile | Low | Simplifies UX for single-location clients |
| 🔴 **P1** | Replace `StarOff` icon with explicit "Set Default" label/button | Very Low | Eliminates discoverability issue |
| 🟡 **P2** | Add ADMIN branch switcher in top navigation bar | Medium | Unlocks cross-branch visibility |
| 🟡 **P2** | Enforce `branchId` as a proper FK on all transaction entities (not raw `Long`) | Medium | Data integrity across modules |
| 🟢 **P3** | Auto-populate branch fields from Company Profile when in single-branch mode | Medium | Reduces setup friction for new deployments |
| 🟢 **P3** | Branch-specific logo/stamp on print templates (partially done per conversation `e39c1f47`) | Medium | Premium branding for multi-branch |

